code: @Override protected NodeInfo<And> info() {     return NodeInfo.create(this, And::new, left(), right()). }
@Override protected And replaceChildren(Expression newLeft, Expression newRight) {     return new And(source(), newLeft, newRight). }
@Override public And swapLeftAndRight() {     return new And(source(), right(), left()). }
@Override public Or negate() {     return new Or(source(), new Not(source(), left()), new Not(source(), right())). }
